Module jakarta.nosql.keyvalue
Package jakarta.nosql.keyvalue

Interface KeyValueTemplate

All Superinterfaces:
Template
public interface KeyValueTemplate extends Template
KeyValueTemplate is a helper class that increases productivity when performing common Bucket operations. Includes integrated object mapping between documents and POJOs.
